---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout title="Refund Policy — Prestique" description="Prestique's refund and cancellation policy.">
  <Nav />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-blog">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-p-muted text-sm mb-12">Last updated: March 29, 2026</p>

      <p>This policy covers refunds and cancellations for Prestique LLC services.</p>

      <h2>Setup Fees</h2>
      <p>Setup fees are non-refundable once work has begun. Work is considered to have begun upon delivery of the first project milestone or seven days after the project kickoff date, whichever comes first.</p>
      <p>If you cancel before work begins, you are entitled to a full refund of the setup fee.</p>

      <h2>Monthly Retainer</h2>
      <p>Monthly retainers may be cancelled at any time with 30 days' written notice sent to <a href="mailto:support@prestique.ai">support@prestique.ai</a>. No refund is issued for the current billing period — service continues through the end of that period and cancellation takes effect at the next billing date.</p>

      <h2>Free Audit Tool</h2>
      <p>The AI audit tool is provided free of charge. No payment is required and no refund policy applies.</p>

      <h2>Exceptional Circumstances</h2>
      <p>We review refund requests outside of this policy on a case-by-case basis. If you believe your situation warrants an exception, reach out and we will do our best to find a fair resolution.</p>

      <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
      <p>Email <a href="mailto:support@prestique.ai">support@prestique.ai</a> with your name, project details, and the reason for your request. We will respond within 5 business days.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Prestique LLC<br />North Carolina, United States<br /><a href="mailto:support@prestique.ai">support@prestique.ai</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
